The people have 4 different jobs:  mechanic, police-officer, project-manager, scientist
City: london, boston, edinburgh, berlin
 1. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 2. the scientist is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 3. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
 4. the person drinking sprite is the person traveling to edinburgh##1
 5. the person who's hobby is cooking is not the person traveling to london##6
 6. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking soy-milk##5
 7. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the project-manager##1
 8. the police-officer is somewhere between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
 9. the police-officer is the person traveling to london##1
10. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
11. the mechanic is not the person traveling to london##6

.:: Answer ::.
