.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-7-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, cooking, hiking, singing
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, march, october, december
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, pony, rabbit, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, rowing, skiing, water-polo
 1. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cricket##5
 2. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 3. the person who's sport is rowing is the owner of the snake##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's hobby is cooking##2
 5. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5
 6. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's hobby is baking##7
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in march##5
 8. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
10. the owner of the pony is on the far right##1
11. the person who's sport is skiing is in an even position##4
12. the person who's birthday is in january is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Hobby   | singing      | hiking     | cooking   | baking    |
| Birthday     | december | october   | march | january |
| Pet     | snake        | rabbit     | goldfish  | pony      |
| Sport   | rowing       | water-polo | cricket   | skiing    |

 